Summary: Low, extremely fast moving chevron shaped craft. No sound.
divs: Sighting DetailsWe were in our back yard in Olivette, Missouri and looking NE when we saw an object moving quickly towards us heading SW under the cloud deck. It was moving extremely fast. We had observed small commercial jets flying overhead all night and this moved 4 to 5 times more quickly than these jets. This happened at 9:20 PM. It had a gray glow which made it appear just slightly lighter than the sky. It made no sound.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Olivette
